## API
> Limitations of my brain or Svelte don't allow for `as` props or non div wrapped components.

### MenuButton
| Slotted Prop | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| `open` | `boolean` <br> Whether or not the Menu is open. |

### MenuItem
| Slotted Prop | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| `active` | `boolean` <br> Whether or not the item is the active/focused item in the list. |